wallet.add.card.learn.more.message:
talabat does not store your card information.

Any payment data that you enter is passed to a payment processor via a secure socket layer (SSL) that encrypts all your information.

The payment processor tokenize your information(substituting your sensitive information with a non-sensitive equivalent).

The payment processor handles your information with a high industry security standard, as it is PCI compliant.

ghc_login_action_description:
We noticed that you are a guest user, and as much as we are happy with your visit and order, we need you to register to create your own account with Talabat so we can serve you better.

If you create your own account with talabat using the same phone number you placed your guest order with, our systems will automatically connect all your current and previous orders you placed using that phone number, and we will be able to help and support you instantly.

After few easy registration steps, you will be able to unlock the full potential of your account by benefiting from all the discounts and promotions we offer, enjoy our loyality and subscription programs, as well as enjoying the best experience we can offer you!
